        "text": "Hi all! My name is George, and I am a faculty member at the University of Utah's Division of Epidemiology. I've been coding in R for about 17 years now. I have a handful of R packages on CRAN, including `epiworldR`, `netdiffuseR`, `rgexf`, `fmcmc`, `slurmR`, `ergmito`, and `ABCoptim`. I love creating tools that others can use.\n\nI just want to connect more with the R community and would love to collaborate with others and contribute to this fantastic community :slightly_smiling_face:.\n\n<https:\/\/ggvy.cl>",
